{"tid":1125832,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Michael Wolf死左","createTime":"2019-04-26T03:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T14:17:15.000Z","uid":45252,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b0e1ac66f9f668dc8dd452a02117ce47d91b50","tid":1125832,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190426/59531294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F59531294&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=f29262a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F59531294&h=dd60c920\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190426/59531294</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想註冊蘋果嘅Android user可以用下面個app<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/paulwongkwan/AccessibleApple/releases\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fpaulwongkwan%2FAccessibleApple%2Freleases&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=912ce092\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/paulwongkwan/AccessibleApple/releases</a><br />\n<br />\n在香港居住和工作超過20年、拍攝無數香港密集樓景以及後巷風景的德裔攝影師Michael Wolf，昨日突然於其長洲寓所離世，終年65歲。曾與Michael Wolf合作舉行回顧展的荷蘭海牙攝影博物館（Fotomuseum Den Haag）昨宣佈有關消息。<br />\n出生於1954年的德國慕尼黑，Michael Wolf在美國和加拿大長大，其後擔任攝影記者，在1994年起他開始香港工作和生活，而香港就成為了他創作的靈感來源，當中以攝影集Architecture of Density (2003 &ndash; 2014)最為人所認識。<br />\n2017年與Michael Wolf合作舉辦名為「城市生活」攝影展的海牙攝影博物館，在聲明中表揚Michael Wolf過去對攝影界的貢獻，指Michael Wolf曾贏得多個國際獎項，而其作品也在紐約藝術博物館、芝加哥當代攝影博物館以及阿姆斯特丹國立博物館等展出。"},{"pid":"11b48770a954bd7ae3bb216ccfe09bd9f831c02d","tid":1125832,"uid":28604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"我成日睇佢嘅相<br />\n<br />\n真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5caff09d4ec9a555024097601fd2239118d44ea","tid":1125832,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110545aef31323772d4fea1afbd555ed354d249f","tid":1125832,"uid":249562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"901d6ca289fa4af01c484753788a3d432f74227a","tid":1125832,"uid":249562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f02d345b642207ff3c04063ede4e23d8137542a","tid":1125832,"uid":217509,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fda916b0035e23c12e59f1eeb65ef0f8c791fab1","tid":1125832,"uid":193602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9971eacade4c0ffb373c6cbfe5cbb1562246daf6","tid":1125832,"uid":250415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"abd7ce74d14841736b7173ad40fc2e99ff3104f2","tid":1125832,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:41:15.000Z","msg":"唔係掛"},{"pid":"2370e37aff697a564e4bdc9288e641837a557aa3","tid":1125832,"uid":89123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢影既題材令到好多人模仿，<br />\n海山樓亦因為佢多年前影既一張相先咁出名"},{"pid":"b690900777e34411a478bb020caf01e98ef225d2","tid":1125832,"uid":117044,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f99b7c5443d4e8c5d108a49d6bdb7a85354075b6","tid":1125832,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pi